Package com.salesforce.multicloudj.common.service

Interface SdkService

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AsyncBlobStore, AwsSdkService, BlobStore
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAsyncBlobStore, AbstractBlobClient, AbstractBlobStore, AliBlobClient, AliBlobStore, AwsAsyncBlobStore, AwsBlobClient, AwsBlobStore, BlobStoreAsyncBridge, GcpAsyncBlobStore, GcpBlobStore
    public interface SdkService
    Base interface for services backed by substrate-specific implementations. This provides a minimal set of methods such as exception translation.
